#----------------------------------------------------------------------
# backup.sh
#----------------------------------------------------------------------

This script can be used to do backups from local filesystem and mysql database to remote filesystem using nfs or samba protocol.

It runs on FreeBSD, Ubuntu (Debian) and Centos (RedHat) systems.

A lot of options are adjustable in config file but not all. For example it's possible you have to set proper paths in mount commands, depend on settings on backup server.

#----------------------------------------------------------------------
